==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Katabolism
<hw>Ka*tab"o*lism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ down +
<?/ to throw.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Destructive or downward
metabolism; regressive metamorphism; same as <er>catabolism</er> (now
the more common spelling); -- opposed to <contr>anabolism</contr>. See
<er>Disassimilation</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Katastate</ent>⟦br⟧
